40:15.726 --> 40:17.561
Good job, man.
Great job.

40:17.561 --> 40:18.645
Thank you.
Don't forget to vote.

40:18.645 --> 40:21.023
Don't forget to vote at all.
Thank you.

40:21.023 --> 40:23.984
[ Indistinct conversations ]

40:23.984 --> 40:26.778
♪ Ooh, ooh ♪

