41:17.120 --> 41:19.831
He will never see
a jail cell.

41:19.831 --> 41:23.001
Well, you're not
becoming a C.I.

41:23.001 --> 41:24.878
What about attorney‐client
privilege?

41:24.878 --> 41:27.172
That could get you
disbarred.

41:27.172 --> 41:31.551
Some things are hard to do.
Some things are scary.

41:31.551 --> 41:35.555
This is both,
but it's something I have to do.

41:35.555 --> 41:39.434
It's not for me, it's for you.
And Jack.

41:39.434 --> 41:41.687
So, look, Angela,
I've already got calls in

41:41.687 --> 41:45.065
to the State's Attorney General
and District Attorney.

41:45.065 --> 41:46.775
They already got a game plan,

41:46.775 --> 41:50.529
and I will personally oversee
how Wesley is utilized.

41:50.529 --> 41:52.406
I promise.

41:52.406 --> 41:55.117
I will do everything humanly
possible to keep him safe.

41:55.117 --> 41:58.036
♪♪

41:58.036 --> 42:00.205
I need you to tell me
this is okay.

42:00.205 --> 42:02.624
I won't do it
without your support.

42:02.624 --> 42:06.586
♪♪

42:06.586 --> 42:08.213
We can't screw this up.

42:08.213 --> 42:09.589
♪♪

42:09.589 --> 42:13.176
Not a single mistake. Not one.

